---
export const prerender = true;
---

<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Case Study: Valentina Russo BG5 · Marco Munich Dev</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Case study del sito valentinarussobg5.com: Human Design Coach & Business Strategist. Stack moderno, AI integrata, due percorsi utente distinti." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --bg: #141C1F;
      --bg-card: #1A2225;
      --border: #243035;
      --text: #E2DED6;
      --text-muted: #8A9699;
      --primary: #C17F3A;
      --primary-hover: #D4944D;
      --accent: #C17F3A;
      --navbar-bg: rgba(20, 28, 31, 0.8);
      --glow: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.06);
      --ai-bg: #0f1629;
      --ai-border: #1e3a5f;
      --browser-bar: #1a1f2e;
      --browser-dot-red: #ff5f57;
      --browser-dot-yellow: #febc2e;
      --browser-dot-green: #28c840;
    }
    [data-theme="light"] {
      --bg: #F5F0E8;
      --bg-card: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #EDE8DF;
      --text: #1E2B2F;
      --text-muted: #6B7B7F;
      --primary: #A0614A;
      --primary-hover: #8A5240;
      --accent: #A0614A;
      --navbar-bg: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.8);
      --glow: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.04);
      --ai-bg: #f0f4ff;
      --ai-border: #bfdbfe;
      --browser-bar: #e5e7eb;
      --browser-dot-red: #ff5f57;
      --browser-dot-yellow: #febc2e;
      --browser-dot-green: #28c840;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── Navbar ── */
    .navbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: var(--navbar-bg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .navbar-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      height: 64px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--primary); }
    .nav-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.75rem;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      transition: color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
    .theme-toggle {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .theme-toggle:hover { border-color: var(--primary); color: var(--primary); }
    [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .icon-sun { display: none; }
    [data-theme="dark"] .theme-toggle .icon-moon { display: inline; }
    [data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .icon-sun { display: inline; }
    [data-theme="light"] .theme-toggle .icon-moon { display: none; }
    .nav-toggle {
      display: none;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
    .nav-toggle span {
      display: block;
      width: 22px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--text);
      margin: 5px 0;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    /* ── Section base ── */
    .section { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    .container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .section-text {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 55vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 8rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 720px; }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--primary);
      background: var(--glow);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Lora', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2.75rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero h1 em {
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .hero-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .hero-link:hover {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* ── Divider ── */
    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 860px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    /* ── Browser mockup ── */
    .browser-frame {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
      max-width: 680px;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .browser-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      background: var(--browser-bar);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .browser-dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-right: 0.75rem;
    }
    .browser-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .browser-dot.red { background: var(--browser-dot-red); }
    .browser-dot.yellow { background: var(--browser-dot-yellow); }
    .browser-dot.green { background: var(--browser-dot-green); }
    .browser-url {
      flex: 1;
      background: var(--bg);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .browser-body {
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .browser-body .site-title {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .browser-body .site-tagline {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .browser-body .site-paths {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .browser-body .site-path {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary);
      background: var(--glow);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    }

    /* ── Sfida cards ── */
    .challenge-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .challenge-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .challenge-card .card-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .challenge-card h3 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .challenge-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Stack tags ── */
    .stack-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .stack-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .stack-card h3 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .stack-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── AI section ── */
    .ai-section {
      background: var(--ai-bg);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--ai-border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ai-border);
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .ai-highlight {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--ai-border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .ai-highlight h3 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .ai-highlight p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .ai-highlight p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .ai-example {
      background: var(--bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.25rem 0;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .ai-example .label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .ai-example .arrow {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin: 0.75rem 0;
    }
    .ai-acronym-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .ai-acronym {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .ai-acronym .tag {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .ai-acronym p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Results ── */
    .results-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .result-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .result-card .result-value {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .result-card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .result-card.full-width {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .cta-section p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      text-align: center;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }
    .footer a {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .footer a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        top: 64px; left: 0; right: 0;
        flex-direction: column;
        background: var(--navbar-bg);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        gap: 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
      .nav-toggle { display: block; }
      .hero { min-height: auto; padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .hero-subtitle { font-size: 1.05rem; }
      .section { padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; }
      .section-title { font-size: 1.5rem; }
      .challenge-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .challenge-card { width: 100% !important; }
      .stack-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .stack-card { width: 100% !important; }
      .ai-acronym-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .ai-acronym { width: 100% !important; }
      .results-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .result-card { width: 100% !important; }
      .browser-frame { margin: 1.5rem auto 0; }
      .browser-body { padding: 1.5rem 1rem; }
      .browser-body .site-paths { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
      .cta-section h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <a href="/dev/" class="nav-logo">Marco Munich <span>&middot; Dev</span></a>
      <div class="nav-right">
        <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
          <li><a href="/dev/come-lavoro">Come Lavoro</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/vibe-coding">Vibe Coding</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/prezzi">Prezzi</a></li>
          <li><a href="/dev/contatti">Contatti</a></li>
        </ul>
        <button class="theme-toggle" id="theme-toggle" aria-label="Cambia tema">
          <span class="icon-sun">&#9728;</span>
          <span class="icon-moon">&#127769;</span>
        </button>
        <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Menu" id="navToggle">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-badge">Case Study</div>
      <h1>Valentina Russo <em>BG5</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Human Design Coach & Business Strategist</p>
      <a href="https://valentinarussobg5.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hero-link">
        valentinarussobg5.com &#8599;
      </a>

      <!-- Browser mockup -->
      <div class="browser-frame">
        <div class="browser-bar">
          <div class="browser-dots">
            <div class="browser-dot red"></div>
            <div class="browser-dot yellow"></div>
            <div class="browser-dot green"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="browser-url">valentinarussobg5.com</div>
        </div>
        <div class="browser-body">
          <div class="site-title">Valentina Russo</div>
          <div class="site-tagline">Human Design Coach & BG5 Business Strategist</div>
          <div class="site-paths">
            <div class="site-path">Privati</div>
            <div class="site-path">Corporate</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <!-- Il Progetto -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Il Progetto</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Due mondi professionali, un solo sito</h2>
      <p class="section-text">
        Valentina Russo lavora come Human Design Coach e Business Strategist attraverso il metodo BG5, e si rivolge a due pubblici diversi: da un lato le persone che vogliono comprendere il proprio design individuale, dall'altro le aziende che cercano strumenti concreti per migliorare la dinamica dei propri team e delle proprie strutture organizzative.
      </p>
      <p class="section-text">
        Il sito doveva riflettere questa doppia identit&agrave; in modo funzionale, con due percorsi completamente separati per Privati e Corporate, ciascuno con la propria navigazione, il proprio tono di voce e i propri contenuti, senza che l'utente si trovasse mai in un'area che non lo riguarda direttamente.
      </p>
      <p class="section-text">
        Allo stesso tempo, la coerenza visiva tra le due sezioni doveva restare intatta, perch&eacute; il brand di Valentina &egrave; uno solo e deve comunicare la stessa solidit&agrave; professionale indipendentemente dal percorso scelto dal visitatore.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <!-- La Sfida Tecnica -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">La Sfida Tecnica</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Requisiti del progetto</h2>
      <div class="challenge-grid">
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="card-icon">&#128268;</div>
          <h3>Due aree distinte</h3>
          <p>Contenuti e navigazione separati per Privati e Corporate, con tono e struttura specifici per ciascun pubblico.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="card-icon">&#9997;&#65039;</div>
          <h3>Blog autonomo</h3>
          <p>Valentina doveva poter scrivere e pubblicare articoli senza intermediari e senza competenze tecniche di alcun tipo.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="card-icon">&#9889;</div>
          <h3>Performance elevate</h3>
          <p>Il sito doveva caricarsi in tempi ridotti senza dipendere da WordPress o piattaforme che aggiungono peso e complessit&agrave; inutile.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-card">
          <div class="card-icon">&#128736;&#65039;</div>
          <h3>Zero manutenzione</h3>
          <p>Il sistema doveva funzionare in autonomia, senza database da gestire, plugin da aggiornare o server da monitorare.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <!-- Stack Tecnologico -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Stack Tecnologico</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Tecnologie utilizzate</h2>
      <div class="stack-grid">
        <div class="stack-card">
          <h3>Grav CMS</h3>
          <p>Sistema di gestione contenuti flat-file che non richiede database, con tempi di risposta minimi e interfaccia di scrittura accessibile anche a chi non ha competenze tecniche.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-card">
          <h3>Vite MPA</h3>
          <p>Build tool moderno configurato in modalit&agrave; multi-page per generare asset ottimizzati, con code splitting automatico e tempi di build ridotti.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-card">
          <h3>GitHub Actions CI/CD</h3>
